  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3570889/" class="title-link">意在其事而不在其文~</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3570889"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/cyn427/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u43416252-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/cyn427/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">cyn</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-08-20"
      class="main-meta">2010-08-20 10:01:51</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3570889_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  作为小说来看，作者并不精道，而且在排版打字方面还有不少错漏。 但我真正想看的也是书中所叙述的特种兵经历，当只是看完故事时还觉得有点“武侠小说”的性质，但看了书后所附的特种兵普及知识后则确信书中看似夸张的描述其实确有其事！ 真的非常佩服特战队员们！

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
